<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l6">Mıchel Beheim vnd Stepfan <expan>ſchul<ex>er</ex></expan> getreẅhender vnd <expan>auſʒrıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l8">ſüllen etc / das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> die <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l9"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> für vns beſandt / vnd <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mıt Jn <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt / daʒ ſıe <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l10"><expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ſelb <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> tun <expan>ſülle<ex>n</ex></expan> . Deẅht <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> . daʒ </ab>
