</div>
<div type="cedula"><ab facs="#facs_272_line_1593760655172_141">Cettula <expan>ınt<ex>er</ex>cluſa</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_272_line_1593760664359_146"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns denn <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
