<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l21">
<add><ab facs="#facs_272_line_1577193546914_2343">daʒ wır noch nıht </ab><ab facs="#facs_272_line_1577193549357_2348">anders wıſſen </ab></add> denn daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> erber <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> / dıe von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> auf <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> tag reıten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l26">wırdt / auf nu ertag 
<del rend="strikethrough">ʒu nacht </del>
