</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_272" id="135r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Winsheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch etlich ewr
                                <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan>
                        fürbracht <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        Kumpfen geschefts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, des unser
                                <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> Michel Beheim und Stepfan
                                <expan>Schul<ex>er</ex></expan> getrewhender und
                                <expan>auszricht<ex>er</ex></expan> sein süllen etc., das
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> die
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> für uns besandt und
                            <expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mit in <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        geredt, daz sie <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> selb <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ein
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> tun <expan>sülle<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                        Dewht <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>, daz sie
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> zu den
                            <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> icht <expan>zuspreche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan>, so wellen wir in
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> iren <expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        mit <expan>ire<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gwalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        slewnigs <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim sein on geverd. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab>Cettula <expan>int<ex>er</ex>clusa</expan>: <expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns denn
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> gen Wesel etc., also
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> botten
                        seid <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> und von
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnötig<ex>en</ex></expan> geschefts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        niht ee <expan>könne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan>, das wellet in gut versteen, und tun
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, <add>daz
                            wir noch niht anders wissen</add>, denn daz
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> erber <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>,
                        die von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> auf <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> tag
                        reiten wirdt, <app>
<note><q type="date">auf nu ertag</q>20.05.1421</note>
</app>
<add>drey stund auf den tag</add> zu Wirczburg <add>meynen zu sein</add>,
                        und ob ewr <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auf die zeit da sey, so meynen
                        sie dennoch <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan> tags
                            <expan>verr<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>anczureite<ex>n</ex></expan>, da mag sich ewr
                                <expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> wol nach richten.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
